'''小查尔斯·杜安·“查理”·贝克'''（{{lang-en|'''Charles Duane "Charlie" Baker, Jr'''}}, {{bd|1956年|11月13日||}})是一位[[美国|美国]][[商人|商人]]及[[政治家|政治家]]。第72任[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[州长|州长]]，其在2015年1月8日宣誓就职，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Miller|first1=Joshua|title=Charlie Baker takes over as 72d governor of Mass.|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2015/01/08/charlie-baker-take-oath-office-governor-today/kUsixGCsMb0j2wbVpcbOgK/story.html|accessdate=2015-01-09|agency=The Boston Globe|date=2015-01-08|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122105020/https://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2015/01/08/charlie-baker-take-oath-office-governor-today/kUsixGCsMb0j2wbVpcbOgK/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他曾在两任马萨诸塞州州长任内担任[[内阁|内阁]]成员，并在{{link-en|Harvard Pilgrim Health Care|Harvard Pilgrim Health Care}}公司担任[[首席执行官|CEO]]超过10年<ref name="harris">Harris, Elizabeth (November 16, 1999). "New England's health care market comes up for air." ''[[The_Bond_Buyer|The Bond Buyer]]'' '''330''' (30,769): p. 7.</ref>，其曾在2010年作为[[共和黨_(美國)|共和党]]候选人竞选马萨诸塞州州长，但竞选并不成功。<ref name="lehigh">Lehigh, Scot (June 10, 2009). "Is the state political stage set for a rerun of 1990?" ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]'' '''275''' (161): p. A13.</ref><ref>"[http://www.boston.com/news/special/politics/2010/governor/results/ Campaign 2010: Governor | Massachusetts] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/news/special/politics/2010/governor/results/ |date=20160303171727 }}." ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]''. Retrieved November 3, 2010.</ref>

